
Database is based on these conventions: http://wiki.coldbox.org/wiki/DatabaseNamingConventions.cfm#Table_Conventions

API structure is based on http://pages.apigee.com/rs/apigee/images/api-design-ebook-2012-03.pdf

Database:

event
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| eventID | eventName | eventDescription | eventPlace | eventDate | eventCreatedDate | eventUpdatedDate |
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
event_invitation
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| eventInvitationID | eventInvitationStatus | FK_userID | FK_userTargetID | eventInvitationCreatedDate | eventInvitationUpdatedDate |
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
user
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| userID | userName | userMail | userPassword | phone | userCreatedDate | userUpdatedDate |
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
user_group
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| userGroupID | FK_applicantUserID | userGroupName | userGroupCreatedDate | userGroupUpdatedDate |
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
user_friendship
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| userFriendshipID | FK_applicantUserID | FK_targetUserID | userFriendshipIsAccepted | userFriendshipCreatedDate |
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
user_friendship_group
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| userFriendshipGroupID | FK_userGroupID | FK_applicantUserID | FK_targetUserID | userFriendshipGroupCreatedDate | userFriendshipGroupUpdatedDate |
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------